      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众云童引多福星君、多禄星君、多寿星君同上。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00002",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同新水令",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "多福多寿比嵩山，多添上寿无算。多祥多瑞霭，多多送吉言。多喜多欢，自俺这多福寿当呈献，多福寿当呈献。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00003",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "同念",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "紫草千秋气象新，桃花万树映琼林。寿酒金樽仙掌露，斑衣笑舞玉堂春。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00004",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君"
      ],
      "text": "我乃多福星君是也。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00005",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "多禄星君"
      ],
      "text": "我乃多禄星君是也。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00006",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "我乃多寿星君是也。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00007",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "为群仙之领袖，祝福之天官。今当下界福主，庆赏芳辰，为此特约九如大仙，前往庆祝。众云童！",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00008",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众云童同允。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00009",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "就此驾云前往。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00010",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众云童"
      ],
      "text": "领法旨。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00011",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同驻马听",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "多喜盈门遍，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00012",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "九如仙同上。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00013",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同驻马听",
      "speakers": [
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "善门人福德双全。看白猿祝寿，仙桃呈献。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00014",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "三位星君在上，我等稽首。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00015",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "列位大仙少礼。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00016",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "三位星君相召，有何见谕？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00017",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "今当下界福主，庆赏芳辰，为此特约列位大仙，前往庆祝。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00018",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "既然如此，一同驾云前往。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00019",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同胡十八",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君",
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "多愿寿而安，多来福耀盈门遍，多来福耀盈门遍。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00020",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众云童"
      ],
      "text": "已到寿筵前。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00021",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "就将仙桃筵前呈献者。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00022",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同胡十八",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "如仙样寿筵间，喜则喜，如阜如川。羡则羡，如愿如缘，如同那寿柏松延。寿柏松延，寿献当前，如同那鹤鹿高眠。寿比陈搏，富贵神仙，富贵神仙。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00023",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "各样切末同舞献。〖吹打〗。各样切末同下。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00024",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同折桂令",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君",
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "瑞云中万福盘旋，彩云缥缈响竹连。庆云缭绕当街献，紫气东来，祥云片片照庭前，祥云片片照庭前。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00025",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君",
        "九如仙"
      ],
      "text": "祝寿已毕。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00026",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "多福星君",
        "多禄星君",
        "多寿星君"
      ],
      "text": "众位大仙各归洞府。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02001002_e00027",
      "play_id": "02001002",
      "scene_id": "02001002_s01",
